cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.CL. 

This paper is a primer on description logics (DLs), which are a subfield of artificial intelligence (AI) and knowledge representation. Therefore, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. DLs also have connections to logic (cs.LO), databases (cs.DB), software engineering (cs.SE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL), which make these sub-categories likely as well.
